#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:8
msgid "`libxml2` and `libxslt` system libraries (required by lxml)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:10
msgid "On Debian/Ubuntu:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:12
msgid "sudo apt-get install libxml2-dev libxslt-dev"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:16
msgid "On macOS (Homebrew):"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:18
msgid "brew install libxml2 libxslt"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:24
msgid "Setup"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:26
msgid ""
"cd serve_api\n"
"\n"
"# Create and activate a virtual environment\n"
"python -m venv venv\n"
"source venv/bin/activate   # Windows: venv\\Scripts\\activate\n"
"\n"
"# Install runtime dependencies\n"
"pip install -r requirements.txt\n"
"\n"
"# Install dev dependencies (pytest, httpx, etc.)\n"
"pip install -r requirements-dev.txt"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:42
msgid "Running the development server"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:44
msgid "From the `serve_api/` directory:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:46
msgid "fastapi dev src/serve.py"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:50
msgid ""
"The server starts on `http://127.0.0.1:8000`. The Swagger UI is at `http://"
"127.0.0.1:8000/docs`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:52
msgid ""
"!!! note \"Working directory\" `serve.py` uses relative paths to load `./"
"data/cprmvmethods.ttl`, `./data/cprmv.ttl`, and `./respec/`. The server must "
"be started from `serve_api/`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:57
msgid "Running tests"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:59
msgid "python -m pytest -vv"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:63
msgid ""
"The CI pipeline also runs a compile check and import check before pytest:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:65
msgid ""
"python -m py_compile src/serve.py\n"
"python -c \"from src.serve import app; print('FastAPI app imported "
"successfully')\""
msgstr ""

